item.title: About
item.description: About Me Hi! I’m Mark and welcome to my cyber security blog! To provide some context, I am a Cyber Security Degree Apprentice with about a year and a half of industry experience, primarily working in the defence sector. I’m right at the beginning of my career so what better way to log my progress than through a blog!? Objectives Throughout the site, you will hopefully find educational blogs that cover a vast range the cyber security.
